hemently. Unlike big box soap, we use no lathering agents, no hardening agents, no fillers, and absolutely no artificial dyes or fragrance. Ingredients that we DO use is our soaps are: plant-based-skin-loving oils, natural clays and botanicals for color, and only pure essential oils for antimicrobial and aromatherapy properties. Personally, we read ingredients labels and we encourage our customers to do the same. You’ll most definitely find us standing on the soap-box about this issue!<br></span></p></div></div><div class=" grid__column" style="padding: 15px;"><div id="_ZxnMCzd" class="_PNdBOk _ZxnMCzd"><picture id="_ndqDuaE" class="_4nlEB5 _ndqDuaE" data-event="{}"><img src="https://media.pagefly.io/file/get/screen-shot-20171104-at-100024-pmpng-1509859414223.png"></picture></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id="_l8GPfDg" class="_gL_BzW _l8GPfDg pb-grid pb-grid--stackable pb-grid--aligned-center pb-grid--automatic"><div class=" grid__column" style="padding: 15px;"><div id="_25VMC_3" class="_PNdBOk _25VMC_3"><picture id="_g0Jjsdk" class="_4nlEB5 _g0Jjsdk" data-event="{}"><img src="https://media.pagefly.io/file/get/screen-shot-20171104-at-95940-pmpng-1509859440961.png"></picture></div></div><div class=" grid__column" style="padding: 15px;"><div id="_VAnBiOG" class="_PNdBOk _VAnBiOG"><div id="_JwQYfyg" class="_gL_BzW _JwQYfyg pb-grid pb-grid--stackable pb-grid--automatic"><div class=" grid__column" style="padding: 15px;"><div id="_z3xOFZV" class="_PNdBOk _z3xOFZV"><h3 id="_LLB7UPa" class="_Y6RW61 _LLB7UPa" data-event="{}"><span class="_rmEgn4 _PMw4hNq _JdPm85">Packaging</span></h3><p id="_NozBiMX" class="_DOoN23 _NozBiMX"><span class="_rmEgn4 _G9_LUN1 _Gwmb_O">When it comes to our packaging, we have taken a minimalist approach. We want the quality of our product to be what you’re paying for, not the package it comes in. We also want our packaging to have as little environmental impact as possible. Because of this, we us only minimal, recyclable, and compostable packaging materials.<br></span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id="_v1oaCJR" class="_gL_BzW _v1oaCJR pb-grid pb-grid--stackable pb-grid--aligned-center pb-grid--automatic"><div class=" grid__column" style="padding: 15px;"><div id="_qDe0cLn" class="_PNdBOk _qDe0cLn"><h3 id="_OkKzSk3" class="_Y6RW61 _OkKzSk3" data-event="{}"><span class="_rmEgn4 _dDbycZq _JdPm85">1% For The Planet</span></h3><p id="_Z13nt1w" class="_DOoN23 _Z13nt1w"><span class="_rmEgn4 _NzWrSKN _Gwmb_O">Mountain Time Soap has joined the “1% For The Planet” movement and have committed 1% of our annual gross sales to local Non-Profit Organizations in Colorado who share our passion for preserving our environment! We understand the responsibility to give back to our Planet and our community, and it is our mission to do so. Learn more at onepercentfortheplanet.org<br></span></p></div></div><div class=" grid__column" style="padding: 15px;"><div id="_de96uJX" class="_PNdBOk _de96uJX"><picture id="_9avoSA_" class="_4nlEB5 _9avoSA_" data-event="{}"><img src="https://media.pagefly.io/file/get/member_verticallogo_colorpng-1509912854800.png"></picture></div></div></div></div></section><section id="_4ezbC34" class="_xNa4NB _4ezbC34"><div class="_xNa4NB__container" style="max-width: 1300px;"><div id="_p784c9r" class="_gL_BzW _p784c9r pb-grid pb-grid--stackable pb-grid--automatic"><div class=" grid__column" style="padding: 15px;"><div id="_oL_vHoN" class="_PNdBOk _oL_vHoN"><h3 id="_9gvyfG1" class="_Y6RW61 _9gvyfG1" data-event="{}"><span class="_rmEgn4 _LPpwCby _JdPm85">Follow Our Adventure On Instagram<br></span></h3><h3 id="_NlwnCXK" class="_Y6RW61 _NlwnCXK" data-event="{}"><span class="_rmEgn4 _EzlqS9R _JdPm85">@mountaintimesoap<br></span></h3></div></div></div><div id="_VA0BiaL" class="_gL_BzW _VA0BiaL pb-grid pb-grid--stackable pb-grid--automatic"><div class=" grid__column" style="padding: 15px;"><div id="_6Q_gtEl" class="_PNdBOk _6Q_gtEl"><div id="_O4xOSlw" class="_b5DMPd _O4xOSlw _O4xOSlw-instagra